## Key QMS Processes

### Document Control
- All quality documents controlled
- Version control and approval
- Accessible to those who need them
- Regular review and update

### Training
- Quality training for all new hires
- Role-specific quality training
- Training records maintained
- Competency verification

### Internal Audits
- Annual audit schedule
- All processes audited annually
- Findings tracked and closed
- Results reported to management

### Nonconformance Management
- All issues logged
- Root cause investigation
- Corrective actions implemented
- Effectiveness verified

### Management Review
- Quarterly reviews
- Data-driven discussion
- Decisions documented
- Actions tracked
